---
title: Butter Bean and Cavolo Nero Stew with Pesto and Ciabatta
description: Looking for a quick and tasty midweek dinner option? Try cooking up our Butter Bean and Cavolo Nero Stew in just 20-25 minutes for a delicious and speedy meal.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_R17_W33_UK_UQ16703-7_Main_high-b2d6e089.jpg
